_sText:
This is my first official xc map, not to make it a walk in the park I added a few hard things (like 1 jump that you have to perform backwards). I couldnt really make a good screeny of how big the map is because of the lighting and alot of jumps close to each other. I also added the "task - treat"-system into my map: after you complete a part: turn on the radio and listen some music. Have fun!

P.S.: Everything u need to know about installing is in ->XC_OVERCLIMB.HTM!!<-
